"15:70:5" : {s: 15, a: 70, w: 5, r: "علم", t: "ٱلْعَٰلَمِينَ", l: "عَٰلَمِين", lc: 73, tl: "l-ʿālamīna", lb: "সকল জাতি, সৃষ্টিজগত",e: "the world", b: "সমস্ত জগৎ/সকল জাতি", i: "alam semesta", f: 61, rm: "to mark/sign/distinguish, creations/beings, world, science/learning/knowledge/information, aware/know. By means of which one knows a thing, hence it signifies world or creation, because by it the Creator is known. alim (pl. ulama) - one who is learned/wise or knows."},
